PHASE 1: OPERATOR SUPPLIES CREDENTIALS (5 MINUTES)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Required: 5 GitHub Secrets

⚙️  Command 1: GCP Project ID
    gh secret set GCP_PROJECT_ID
    Value: Your GCP project ID (e.g., "my-project-12345")

⚙️  Command 2: GCP Service Account Key
    gh secret set GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY < /path/to/service-account.json
    Note: Must have Secret Manager admin permissions

⚙️  Command 3: AWS Access Key ID
<REDACTED_SECRET_REMOVED_BY_AUTOMATION>
    Value: Your AWS access key (e.g., "AKIA...")

⚙️  Command 4: AWS Secret Access Key
<REDACTED_SECRET_REMOVED_BY_AUTOMATION>
    Value: Your AWS secret key

⚙️  Command 5: AWS KMS Key ARN (Optional)
    gh secret set AWS_KMS_KEY_ARN
    Value: ARN of your KMS key OR leave empty for auto-provision

