🔐 SECURITY & ARCHITECTURE PROPERTIES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

✅ IMMUTABLE
   - Release tag v2026.03.08-production-ready (permanent reference)
   - GitHub Issue audit comments (timestamped, no edit capability)
   - All artifacts timestamped with commit SHA

✅ EPHEMERAL
   - Zero long-lived API keys
   - OIDC tokens → JWT tokens → cloud provider session tokens only
   - All tokens expire within 1 hour

✅ IDEMPOTENT
   - Terraform dry-run mode for safe planning
   - All scripts support re-execution without side effects
   - Safe to repeat credential provisioning

✅ NO-OPS / FULLY AUTOMATED / HANDS-OFF
   - After credentials supplied: zero manual intervention
   - Daily rotation: automatic
   - Health checks: automatic
   - Error notifications: automatic

✅ GSM, VAULT, KMS INTEGRATION
   - Layer 1 (GSM): Google Secret Manager via Workload Identity Federation
   - Layer 2 (Vault): HashiCorp Vault with JWT auth + policy bundles
   - Layer 3 (KMS): AWS Key Management Service with OIDC assume-role
   - Sequential Fallback: GSM → Vault → KMS (graceful degradation)

